1990 - A Home At The End Of The World
1995 - Flesh and Blood
1999 - The Hours
2005 - Specimen Days
2010 - By Nightfall

2002 - Lands End: A Walk in Provincetown

2000 - Drawn By The Sea (catálogo de exhibición; 110 copias firmadas)
